reviewText:
Both of these films, particularly WILD WOMEN OF WONGO, are presented here with better color values than I've seen on other DVDs.  The prints are the shorter US editions and are full-frame format, but the color is improved from previous transfers of these films.  Both films are trashy fun, but nothing great.

It's nice to see VCI release a new edition of Psychotronica, as it's been a long time since their previous Psychotronica releases.
